Package com.nasdaq.ncdsclient.listeners

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BrokerListener
    This interface allows the caller to define and register a Listener on a Kafka Broker.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PlainListener
    Default implementation.
    SaslPlainListener
    Define and register a SASL_PLAIN listener on a Kafka broker.
    SaslSslListener
    Define and register a SASL_SSL listener on a Kafka broker.
    SslListener
    Define and register an SSL listener on a Kafka broker.
